This is Perl module Plack::Middleware::DBIx::QueryLog.

INSTALLATION

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % git clone git://github.com/dameninngenn/p5-Plack-Middleware-DBIx-QueryLog.git
    % cd p5-Plack-Middleware-DBIx-QueryLog
    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

Plack::Middleware::DBIx::QueryLog documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc Plack::Middleware::DBIx::QueryLog

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

